items.title: Trans youth care ban vetoed by Kansas governor again
items.description: Kansas Governor Laura Kelly vetoed Senate Bill 63, which would have restricted gender-affirming care for transgender youth.

items.description: The filings also provided new insights into DOGE's ongoing mission with the Treasury Department.

items.title: Inflation increased in January, posing obstacle for Trump tariff plans
items.description: Consumer prices rose 3% in January compared to a year ago, data showed.

items.description: "The bloodshed must stop and this war must end," U.S. Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth said.
